security officer, said Gibson.
   Antonio Harold Rosas, 21, a native of Colombia, was arrested by
police who tracked him with a dog and booked him for investigation
of murder, said Gibson. Drug and alcohol tests were performed but
results were not available.
   Officials for Waymar Productions, makers of ``Dead Men Don't
Die'' starring Elliott Gould and Melissa Anderson, said they did
not have enough information about the accident to comment.
